NICHOLAS E. NICOLAIDES and ELMER SARVOY, Partners, doing business as the ANCHOR BAR, v. JAMES T. VOCELLE, Director, State Beverage Department, State of Florida. 36 So. (2nd) 376 July 27, 1948

June Term, 1948

En Banc Mallory H. Horton, and Katz & Fuller, for appellants. Patton & Kanner, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed on authority of Marino v. Vocelle, decided July 27, 1948.

THOMAS, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN, ADAMS, SE-BRING and HOBSON, JJ., concur. BARNS, J., dissents.
